{"tid":1509754,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我想知警察諗緊乜","createTime":"2019-08-27T02:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T03:53:59.000Z","uid":67197,"like":98,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1d096a960d83c612616d01bd01a9e744e65df17e","tid":1509754,"uid":67197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:53:46.000Z","msg":"假設我係佢地<br />\n我真係會幾開心<br />\n以下係幻想<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上全部幻想<br />\n出面班人唔該打少陣飛機<br />\n習慣係一件好恐怖既事<br />\n你地已經習慣左<br />\n警察係可以無編號無委任證<br />\n警察射催淚彈射彈珠你地係接受到既<br />\n警察射盲示威者打到示威者骨折腦出血<br />\n你地譴責兩句就完左件事既<br />\n唔該唔好比習慣磨滅左三個月既努力<br />\n<br />\n無人會幫我地架<br />\n你地幾時明呀<br />\n記者影到既片<br />\n無一個黑警入到罪呀<br />\n人地先可以咁肆無忌憚呀<br />\n速龍跑跑下仆街係咪咁好笑呀<br />\n唔好笑呀 佢唔仆街就有手足比佢捉到啦<br />\n警察跌槍係咪咁好笑呀<br />\n唔好笑呀 佢真係拎支真槍指住我地啦<br />\n<br />\n我再重申一次<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無人會幫我地架</span></strong></span><br />\n西方國家譴責兩句架咋<br />\n搞唔掂咪撤資走囉<br />\n最後都係食自己咋"},{"pid":"47b3dfb49fd5f1489b8cbbfed393778112c16298","tid":1509754,"uid":9116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:54:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">612！721！811！你記得嗎？請香港人繼續走下去！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://im5.ezgif.com/tmp/ezgif-5-d5ebcebba7cd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fim5.ezgif.com%2Ftmp%2Fezgif-5-d5ebcebba7cd.gif&h=5f074275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">27/8(二) 動物界集會/遊行 轉場8.31民陣大遊行</span> </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhAWbhG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhAWbhG.jpg&h=63a1860b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2wsp4CY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2wsp4CY.jpg&h